# NEWS for gpg4win et al.                         -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
# The version numbers given are used by gpg4win and GnuPG [VS-]Desktop


Noteworthy changes in Version 4.4.1 (unreleased)
------------------------------------------------
Additionally, the Noteworthy changes in Version 3.3.0 (of VSD) are new
compared to Version 4.4.0 (of Gpg4win).

--- Bug Fixes ---

(en) Kleopatra: Keyresolver GpgOL, groups are resolved again [T7484]


Noteworthy changes in Version 3.3.3 (unreleased)
------------------------------------------------

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GnuPG:          2.2.50
Kleopatra:      3.3.0
GpgOL:          2.6.4
GpgEX:          1.0.10
Kompendium DE:  4.0.1
Compendium EN:  3.0.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Noteworthy changes in Version 3.3.2 (2025-04-25)
------------------------------------------------

(en) Libgpg-error updated to version 1.54 to fix the UNC regression.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GnuPG:          2.2.47
Kleopatra:      3.3.0
GpgOL:          2.6.0
GpgEX:          1.0.10
Kompendium DE:  4.0.1
Compendium EN:  3.0.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


